column2: UO_MX_CIP : Open tank path to outlet drain line.
UO_MX_CIP : Commence PW Preflush of vessel
UO_MX_CIP : Close MX outlet to flood vessel.
MX_UO_CIP : Wait to reach vessel flood mass
UO_MX_CIP : Commence vessel washing with PW
UO_MX_CIP : Filtration line PW wash completed
UO_MX_CIP : Stop Steaming PW inlet line
MX_UO_CIP : Wait for OPER to setup for WFI
UO_MX_CIP : WFI Rinse complete. Wait to empty vessel.
